  "description": "A wide-angle shot captures a majestic suspension bridge spanning a vibrant blue body of water. The bridge, characterized by its towering concrete support pillars and intricate steel latticework, dominates the scene. Beyond the bridge, a cityscape with buildings and industrial structures stretches along the coastline, nestled against rolling hills in the distance. The water exhibits gentle ripples and reflections, adding depth to the composition. The sky is a clear, pale blue, creating a bright and airy atmosphere.",
